    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Automatica</strong>, a 2D Automation and Factory game inspired by titles like <strong>Shapez</strong> and <strong>Factorio</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Conveyor Belt System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this unique automation game, I've added a twist to the traditional conveyor belt system – <strong>connecting building is now as simple as dragging a line from one node into another</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/2232be36bb861fc8b74e42ef18140595.poster.avif?t=1731244534\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/2232be36bb861fc8b74e42ef18140595.webm?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/2232be36bb861fc8b74e42ef18140595.mp4?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sell Resources for Money</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn money</strong> to place more Nodes by <strong>launching resources into space</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/67fe22659280ada9f53b82f660858cd6.poster.avif?t=1731244534\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/67fe22659280ada9f53b82f660858cd6.webm?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/67fe22659280ada9f53b82f660858cd6.mp4?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Big Research Tree</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock additional Nodes </strong>in the Research Tree using higher-quality resources</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/95f6aeee63abecd3775e1901393e7b14.poster.avif?t=1731244534\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/95f6aeee63abecd3775e1901393e7b14.webm?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/95f6aeee63abecd3775e1901393e7b14.mp4?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You’re the last Hope for Earth</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission? Use machines called <strong>Nodes</strong> to mine various ores and fluids, <strong>helping the people on Earth who have run out of resources</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/e3e84ed21c7462a32041f92ff437e5d6.poster.avif?t=1731244534\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/e3e84ed21c7462a32041f92ff437e5d6.webm?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319060/extras/e3e84ed21c7462a32041f92ff437e5d6.mp4?t=1731244534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thanks :)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I've poured my heart into creating this game</strong>, and I genuinely hope you enjoy it as much as I do. I would greatly appreciate any feedback. &lt;3</p>",
